node.text: Teaching is hard. Really hard. Sundays can be especially stressful as educators gear up for the week. The purpose of the Stress Less Sunday for Educators series will be to help educators be in the best mental space possible for the upcoming week!

node.text:
Any kid will tell you that play dough kits are fun, but do you know the many benefits that sensory play offers? Our friends at @tinkerboxsensory do!

Sensory play supports:
a. fine motor skills
b. language development
c. cognitive growth
d. problem-solving skills
e. social interaction

Which benefit of sensory play surprises you the most? Leave letter a, b, c, d or e in the comments!

Check out their page to order and give them a follow!  Free shipping on any orders over $35.  Click link in bio to purchase.
